N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4215.7 - Mutilated tickets

State Regulations

Mutilated pari-mutuel tickets or those whose validity is
questioned shall be submitted to the New York State Tax Commission for
inspection, and the ruling of said commission thereon shall be final and
conclusive. Notes
